      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys 2022R2, DePuy Synthes internal) operate under documented software quality management systems with version control, issue tracking, and regression test suites. FDA code is subject to 21 CFR Part 11 controls; Ansys is a commercially validated solver with published verification manual; DePuy Synthes internal code carries ISO 13485 SQA controls. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
