      "rationale": "Force residual norms converged to < 1×10⁻⁶ for all load steps. Energy balance error < 0.3% across all 11 model runs. Incremental load stepping (200 steps to full load) confirmed path-independent solution for the quasi-static problem. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
