      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model captures observed nonlinear material behaviour; contact formulation appropriate for screw-rod interface.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa, E_t=3.2 GPa) validated against coupon test data. Penalty-based frictionless contact at screw-rod interface consistent with lubricated bench test conditions. UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate modelled as linear elastic (E=1.0 GPa) matching ASTM F1717 specification material. Model form judged appropriate for the QoI."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
