      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs traceable to measured data; uncertainty bounds quantified.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties derived from 12 tensile coupon specimens machined from production bar stock (same heat as device). Geometric model constructed from CMM measurements of production screws (n=3); nominal geometry used with dimensional tolerance uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (±0.05 mm on critical features). Input uncertainty contribution to QoI uncertainty < 3%."
    },
    {
