      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test samples representative of production devices; traceability documented.",
      "rationale": "N=11 constructs assembled from production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screws (same design history file revision as submission device) and production titanium rods. UHMWPE blocks sourced from single lot meeting ASTM F1717 dimensional requirements. Sample traceability documented in laboratory notebook LN-2022-047."
