      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in FEA replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry: fixed base, 70 mm moment arm, displacement-controlled loading at actuator attachment point. Screw torque pre-load (4 N·m) applied in FEA initial step matching torque wrench setting recorded in bench test protocol. Equivalency confirmed by overlay of FEA and experimental load-displacement curves in the elastic regime."
    },
