    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single factor below required level (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs required 3) is accepted on the basis that the ASTM F1717 standard configuration represents the worst-case bending moment for this construct geometry and that all quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, QoI error < 10%) are satisfied across both laboratories and all three QoIs. The FEA model ensemble is judged credible for the stated COU.",
